-busy-handler","kind":"refusal-memento","reason":"JDBC does not expose a callback-based busy handler; Statement.setQueryTimeout (which this kit DOES bind as concept:sql-busy-timeout) covers the timeout-shaped variant. SQLite's callback-shaped busy handler requires the native org.sqlite extension API, not standard JDBC. Refusing the callback-shaped variant.","surface":"org.sqlite.SQLiteConfig#setBusyTimeout","target_language":"java","would_close_with_cluster":"Callback-based busy-collision handling on >=2 SQL drivers"},"header":{"concept":"concept:sql-busy-handler","kind":"refusal-memento","surface":"org.sqlite.SQLiteConfig#setBusyTimeout","targetLanguage":"java","wouldCloseWithCluster":"Callback-based busy-collision handling on >=2 SQL drivers"},"schemaVersion":"1"}xŗblake3-512:8272400d23ecc38b5ff59798a3e452436b21c57b13a1081078ef7ee18674e094fe360fde3858ae1ee561a4b9863bd0dfe50ae226eb180d3f925f4b3e68d0c93fY	p{"body":{"body_source":{"body_text":"    @ProveKitSugar(\u000a        concept = \"concept:sql-connection-pool-acquire\",\u000a        library = \"sqlite-jdbc\",\u000a        loss = {\"sync-vs-async\", \"pool-sizing-policy\", \"error-handling-model\",\u000a                \"eviction-strategy\"}\u000a    )\u000a    public static Connection acquireFromDataSource(DataSource ds) throws SQLException {\u000a        return ds.getConnection();\u000a    }\u000a","file":"src/main/java/org/provekit/shim/sqlite_jdbc/SqliteJdbcShim.java","source_cid":"blake3-512:4e858ecb222e932d96bf96598af280ddbdbc774fd4dfa4f9b5824f6a6500dcccdf14ebaa6d75538c49ab487d22b75e7e89d17099c19407999e6ad6bb5d6a2348","span":{"end_col":5,"end_line":135,"start_col":4,"start_line":127}},"concept_name":"concept:sql-connection-pool-acquire","kind":"library-sugar-binding-entry","loss_record_contribution":{"form":"literal","value":{"entries":["sync-vs-async","pool-sizing-policy","error-handling-model","eviction-strategy"]}},"param_names":["ds"],"param_types":["javax.sql.DataSource"],"return_type":"java.sql.Conne